==Demographics==
{{expand section|date=August 2015}}
As of the 2020 census there is only 245 people in the town of Bakerhill. With the median age of being 34 years old. About 78% of the population is white and 22% is black.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Census profile: Bakerhill, AL |url=http://censusreporter.org/profiles/16000US0103724-bakerhill-al/ |access-date=January 22, 2024 |website=Census Reporter |language=en}}</ref>{{clear left}}

